Ubiquitous computer usage ka sabse bara faida productivity ka badhna hai. Computer hamen kam mehnat mein zyada kaam karne ki suvidha dete hain, aur wo bhi tez tareen. Further, computerization ke badhne ke saath, security threats aur privacy invasions ka risk bhi badh jata hai.

  "text": "Jab baat marketing ki aati hai, to kamyabi ke ahem elements mein se aik ye hai ke aap ko pata ho ke apne target audience tak kaise pahunchna hai.
